Enum Constants.ImageExportOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Constants.ImageExportOptions>
      • de.gnwi.spicesviewer.Constants.ImageExportOptions
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Constants.ImageExportOptions>
    Enclosing class:
    Constants

    public static enum Constants.ImageExportOptions
extends java.lang.Enum<Constants.ImageExportOptions>
    An enum for the four different modes of exporting the graph or the whole main frame that holds their language-dependent representations.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      FILESINKIMAGES
      Constant for exporting the graph by GraphStream's FileSinkImages.
      GRAPH_ATTRIBUTE
      Constant for exporting the graph by adding an 'ui.screenshot' attribute to it.
      SWING
      Constant for exporting the graph by using the Swing paint() method.
      WHOLE_FRAME
      Constant for screenshotting the whole main frame by using the Swing paint() method.
